f5t:"Ph\xE2n t\xEDch D\u1EE5ng Th\u1EA7n",f5d:"Ph\xE2n t\xEDch Ng\u0169 H\xE0nh \u0111\u1EC3 t\xECm D\u1EE5ng Th\u1EA7n (h\xE0nh c\u1EA7n thi\u1EBFt nh\u1EA5t). Thu h\xFAt n\u0103ng l\u01B0\u1EE3ng t\xEDch c\u1EF1c trong cu\u1ED9c s\u1ED1ng.",
